attributes.title: ROBOTNIK vs WILY
attributes.description: Dr. Robotnik and Dr. Wily go head-to-giant-head in a cybernetic, pixelated death match.

attributes.title: GLaDOS vs. Mother Brain
attributes.description: One's got a brain the size of the internet with a murder/science fetish. The other is a living brain that vomits explosives. Yeah, we had to do a Boss Battle for GLaDOS and Mother Brain.

attributes.title: Sonic vs. Metroid
attributes.description: Sonic's attempt to get into Samus' Mystic Cave Zone is cut short by a battle between Ridley and Metal Overlord.

attributes.title: Solid Snake in Yoshi's Island
attributes.description: Solid Snake searches for enlightenment and finds it without having to sit through fifteen different, 45-minute-long cutscenes.

attributes.title: Darth Vader vs. Dracula
attributes.description: Darth Vader moves to the country, but another dark lord has issues with Vader's parenting style.

attributes.title: Magneto vs. Shredder
attributes.description: Magneto is tricked into thinking there was free pizza at the Colosseum, by Shredder and his crew of flunkies. Shredder reluctantly fights Magneto, and the result is what you'd expect.

attributes.title: Wario vs Goro
attributes.description: Hilarious 8bit Battle between Mario Bros' Wario and Mortal Kombat's Goro.

attributes.title: Boba Fett vs Predator
attributes.description: Epic 8bit fight between Star Wars' Boba Fett and Predator.

attributes.title: Wolverine vs. Spider-Man
attributes.description: Wolverine, who gets triggered by gray pants which we relates to Jean Gray, fights Spider-Man. Who will win?

attributes.title: Dr. Strange vs. Dr. Doom
attributes.description: New movie star Dr. Strange takes on Dr. Doom. Who will win?

attributes.title: Thanos vs. Doomsday
attributes.description: It's Thanos vs Doomsday......who will win?

attributes.title: Wonder Woman Vs. Thor
attributes.description: The Princess of the Amazons, the Goddess of Truth, Wonder Woman battles it out against the son of Odin, Thor. Who will win?

attributes.title: Master Chief Vs. Price
attributes.description: Boss Battles Pins Master Chief and Price against each other!
